Cost-effectiveness of nonsteroidal anti-inflammatory drugs and opioids in the 
treatment of knee osteoarthritis in older patients with multiple comorbidities.

Katz JN(1), Smith SR(2), Collins JE(3), Solomon DH(4), Jordan JM(5), Hunter 
DJ(6), Suter LG(7), Yelin E(8), Paltiel AD(9), Losina E(10).

Author information:
