The K167I variant of DNA polymerase β that is found in Esophageal Carcinoma 
patients impairs polymerase activity and BER.

Wang Y(1), Zang W(1), Du Y(1), Chen X(1), Zhao G(1).

Author information:
(1)College of Basic Medical Sciences, Zhengzhou University, Zhengzhou 450001, 
